Package: shinyQuiz
Title: Create Gradable Quizzes for R Shiny
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Joseph", "Marlo", email = "jpm770@nyu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("George", "Perrett", email = "gp77@nyu.edu", role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: Functions for creating simple, flexible quizzes for R Shiny. Easily create quizzes from various prebuilt question and choice types or create your own using htmltools and shiny as building blocks. Integrates with larger R Shiny applications. Ideal for non-web-developers such as educators, data scientists, and anyone who wants to assess responses interactively.
